{"id":4259,"date":"2025-06-19T11:33:22","date_gmt":"2025-06-19T04:33:22","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4259"},"modified":"2025-06-19T11:33:22","modified_gmt":"2025-06-19T04:33:22","slug":"toner-can-bang-da-dang-xit-gsc","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/toner-can-bang-da-dang-xit-gsc\/","title":{"rendered":"Toner C\u00e2n B\u1eb1ng Da (D\u1ea1ng X\u1ecbt) GSC &#8211; B\u01b0\u1edbc Ch\u0103m S\u00f3c Quan Tr\u1ecdng Cho L\u00e0n Da"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><b><i>Toner c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng da<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n xa l\u1ea1 nh\u01b0ng th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb b\u1ecf qua b\u1edfi nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ecb em. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. Toner \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng cho l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh. C\u00f9ng GSC t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u toner l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m\u00a0<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"toner-la-gi\"><\/span><b>Toner l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Toner l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m cho da sau khi l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1ea7m toner v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc hoa h\u1ed3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, toner kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m t\u1eeb hoa h\u1ed3ng. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, toner l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng &#8220;c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng&#8221; da sau khi t\u1ea9y trang v\u00e0 r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t, gi\u00fap da kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb kh\u00f4 ho\u1eb7c m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"toner-dang-xit-la-gi\"><\/span><b>Toner D\u1ea1ng X\u1ecbt L\u00e0 G\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Toner d\u1ea1ng x\u1ecbt l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn m\u1edbi m\u1ebb so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i toner truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y c\u00f3 v\u00f2i x\u1ecbt ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i, gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng toner l\u00ean da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n b\u00f4ng cotton. Ngo\u00e0i ra, toner d\u1ea1ng x\u1ecbt c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 x\u1ecbt kho\u00e1ng, mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da nhanh ch\u00f3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4303\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4303\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4303\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/50-1.webp\" alt=\"Toner C\u00e2n B\u1eb1ng Da (D\u1ea1ng X\u1ecbt) GSC\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/50-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/50-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/50-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/50-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4303\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>Toner C\u00e2n B\u1eb1ng Da (D\u1ea1ng X\u1ecbt) GSC<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phan-loai-cac-loai-toner-hien-nay\"><\/span><b>Ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i toner hi\u1ec7n nay<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7n nay, toner \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia th\u00e0nh hai lo\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh:<\/span><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Toner kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n: Th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u00e1ng, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi da kh\u00f4 ho\u1eb7c da th\u01b0\u1eddng. Lo\u1ea1i toner n\u00e0y gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da sau khi r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Toner ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n: C\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam, s\u00e1t khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u, th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho da d\u1ea7u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 da m\u1ee5n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"toner-co-that-su-quan-trong-va-can-thiet\"><\/span><b>Toner c\u00f3 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. D\u00f9 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da \u0111\u1eaft ti\u1ec1n nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u00e1c ch\u1ecb em ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 nh\u1edd v\u00e0o quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng, trong \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu b\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng toner.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gsc-moist-soothing-toner-%e2%80%93-toner-lam-diu-va-can-bang-da\"><\/span><b>GSC Moist Soothing Toner &#8211; Toner l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu v\u00e0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng da<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">GSC Moist Soothing Toner l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m toner d\u1ea1ng x\u1ecbt ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb cam th\u1ea3o, tr\u00e0 xanh, l\u00f4 h\u1ed9i, v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n s\u00e2m. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng pH. L\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-chinh\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f4ng D\u1ee5ng Ch\u00ednh<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng k\u00edch \u1ee9ng: Gi\u1ea3m s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 ng\u1ee9a ng\u00e1y tr\u00ean da, mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da: Gi\u00fap l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da sau khi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m v\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da: H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da, gi\u00fap da m\u1ec1m m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng kh\u1ecfe.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn: Gi\u00fap \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da, l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4304\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4304\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4304\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/50-2.webp\" alt=\"GSC Moist Soothing Toner\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/50-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/50-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/50-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/50-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4304\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">GSC Moist Soothing Toner<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thanh-phan-noi-bat\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00e0nh Ph\u1ea7n N\u1ed5i B\u1eadt<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0: Cam th\u1ea3o, tr\u00e0 xanh, l\u00f4 h\u1ed9i, nh\u00e2n s\u00e2m, TBG hoa sen, TBG nho, v\u00e0 di\u1ebfp c\u00e1.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y cung c\u1ea5p d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1c t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-su-dung-toner-dang-xit\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1ch S\u1eed D\u1ee5ng Toner D\u1ea1ng X\u1ecbt<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng sau khi l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da (s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t).<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">X\u1ecbt m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ee7 v\u00e0o b\u00f4ng cotton v\u00e0 lau nh\u1eb9 theo chi\u1ec1u c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac da, sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ed7 nh\u1eb9 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c ng\u00f3n tay \u0111\u1ec3 toner th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y 2 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4305\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4305\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4305\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/50-3.webp\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch S\u1eed D\u1ee5ng Toner D\u1ea1ng X\u1ecbt\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/50-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/50-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/50-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/50-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4305\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch S\u1eed D\u1ee5ng Toner D\u1ea1ng X\u1ecbt<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u01b0u \u00fd: Khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng toner d\u1ea1ng x\u1ecbt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u, h\u00e3y x\u1ecbt t\u1eeb t\u1eeb v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh x\u1ecbt qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. Vi\u1ec7c x\u1ecbt qu\u00e1 nhanh ho\u1eb7c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m hao h\u1ee5t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng da, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u00f9ng da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m nh\u01b0 m\u1eaft.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Toner \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng cho l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh. C\u00f9ng GSC t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u toner l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m\u00a0<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4306,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4259","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4259","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4259"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4259\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4307,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4259\/revisions\/4307"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4306"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4259"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4259"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4259"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}